@startuml opentelemetry-flow
!include <C4/C4_Sequence>
!include <logos/vue>
!include <logos/laravel>

title OpenTelemetry Distributed Tracing Flow

Person(user, "User")
System(vue, "Vue.js")
System(otel_browser, "OTEL Browser SDK")
System(laravel, "Laravel")
System(otel_php, "OTEL PHP SDK")
System_Ext(external_api, "External API")
System(jaeger, "Jaeger")

user -> vue : Click button
activate vue

vue -> otel_browser : startSpan('user.click')
activate otel_browser
otel_browser --> vue : span
vue -> vue : Handle click event

vue -> otel_browser : startSpan('inertia.visit')
otel_browser --> vue : span
vue -> laravel : GET /users (Inertia request)
activate laravel

laravel -> otel_php : startSpan('http.server')
activate otel_php
otel_php --> laravel : span

laravel -> otel_php : startSpan('controller.dashboard')
otel_php --> laravel : span

laravel -> otel_php : startSpan('service.external_api')
otel_php --> laravel : span

laravel -> external_api : GET /users\nAuthorization: Bearer {token}
activate external_api

laravel -> otel_php : setAttribute('http.url', url)
laravel -> otel_php : setAttribute('http.method', 'GET')

external_api --> laravel : 200 OK\n{"data": [...]}
deactivate external_api

laravel -> otel_php : setAttribute('http.status_code', 200)
laravel -> otel_php : endSpan('service.external_api')

laravel -> otel_php : endSpan('controller.dashboard')
laravel -> otel_php : endSpan('http.server')

laravel --> vue : Inertia response (HTML + JSON props)
deactivate laravel

vue -> otel_browser : endSpan('inertia.visit')
vue -> otel_browser : endSpan('user.click')

otel_browser -> jaeger : Export traces\nOTLP HTTP (port 4318)
activate jaeger
deactivate otel_browser

otel_php -> jaeger : Export traces\nOTLP gRPC (port 4317)
deactivate otel_php

vue -> vue : Render data
vue --> user : Display results
deactivate vue

jaeger -> jaeger : Store & index traces
deactivate jaeger

note right of jaeger
  **Trace Visualization:**
  Access: http://localhost:16686

  **Trace Details:**
  • Total duration (frontend + backend)
  • Individual span timings
  • External API latency
  • Cache hit/miss
  • Database queries

  **Attributes:**
  • service.name
  • http.url, http.method
  • http.status_code
  • user.id
  • custom attributes
end note

note right of otel_browser
  **Frontend Instrumentation:**
  • User interactions (clicks, forms)
  • Inertia.js navigation
  • Component lifecycle
  • Fetch/XHR requests

  **Auto-instrumentation:**
  • Document load
  • Resource timing
  • XMLHttpRequest
  • Fetch API
end note

note right of otel_php
  **Backend Instrumentation:**
  • HTTP server (Laravel routes)
  • Database queries (PostgreSQL)
  • Cache operations (Redis)
  • External API calls (Guzzle)
  • Queue jobs

  **Automatic context propagation:**
  Trace ID passed from frontend to backend
end note

@enduml
